overview: Larry Sweeney defends his ICW-ICWA Tex-Arkana Television Championship against F4W's Bryan Alvarez! Eddie Kingston and Hallowicked settle their score in a rare “Falls Count Anywhere” match, while Mitch Ryder and Lince Dorado meet in a lucha de apuesta to end their rivalry. Ryder wagers his hair against the mask of Dorado in the main event!
title: Chikara: Chapter 11
